comment: /**  * Set a single notification type, or a list of notification types  * as comma-delimited String.  */
code: /**  * Set a single notification type, or a list of notification types  * as comma-delimited String.  */ public void setNotificationType(String notificationType) {     this.notificationTypes = StringUtils.commaDelimitedListToStringArray(notificationType). }

comment: /**  * Set a list of notification types.  */
code: /**  * Set a list of notification types.  */ public void setNotificationTypes(@Nullable String... notificationTypes) {     this.notificationTypes = notificationTypes. }

comment: /**  * Return the list of notification types.  */
code: /**  * Return the list of notification types.  */ @Nullable public String[] getNotificationTypes() {     return this.notificationTypes. }

comment: /**  * Set the name of this notification.  */
code: /**  * Set the name of this notification.  */ public void setName(@Nullable String name) {     this.name = name. }

comment: /**  * Return the name of this notification.  */
code: /**  * Return the name of this notification.  */ @Nullable public String getName() {     return this.name. }

comment: /**  * Set a description for this notification.  */
code: /**  * Set a description for this notification.  */ public void setDescription(@Nullable String description) {     this.description = description. }

comment: /**  * Return a description for this notification.  */
code: /**  * Return a description for this notification.  */ @Nullable public String getDescription() {     return this.description. }
